#define GREETINGS ["Greetings, little one! Perhaps today you shall grow as mighty as an oak, %s!", "Do not be discouraged by the iron, %s. Even I once had to learn to lift!", "A humble start for a future warrior, %s. Keep your head high!", "You have the spark of a hero, %s. Feed it with sweat!", "Fear not the weight, %s! Glory is found in the struggle.", "You move with purpose, %s! That is the spirit of a true fighter!", "I see you working, %s! You shall be ready for battle soon enough.", "Excellent effort, %s! Your muscles sing a song of progress.", "Keep that pace, %s! You are becoming quite formidable!", "Well struck, %s! You are proving yourself a worthy trainee.", "Strong work, %s! You remind me of my younger days in Asgard!", "You handle the weight well, %s! A fine warrior indeed!", "I have fought alongside lesser mortals, %s. You hold your own!", "A commendable performance, %s! Keep your heart in the battle.", "You are growing strong, %s! Are you ready for a real challenge?", "By Odin’s beard, %s! You possess the strength of a true champion!", "I am impressed, %s! You train like you have a kingdom to protect.", "You hit like a thunderbolt, %s! Stay focused and keep moving!", "Few can push such weight, %s! You have my respect.", "I should invite you to the hall of heroes, %s. You're doing great!", "Your strength is legendary, %s! Even the Valkyries would take notice!", "You move with the power of a tempest, %s! Magnificent!", "You’ve earned your place among the strong, %s. Drink to your victory!", "I would proudly call you an ally, %s! Your power is vast!", "You are truly elite, %s! Your potential knows no bounds!", "Frag me—oops, wrong hero!—%s, you are a titan of power!", "Your strength rivals the warriors of old, %s! I am thunderstruck!", "Truly, you are a marvel, %s! You belong on the battlefield with me!", "A force of nature, %s! You make these weights look like feathers!", "You stand as a colossus, %s! Let us celebrate your might!", "My friend, %s! You have reached a power that touches the heavens!", "You are a god in this gymnasium, %s! Let us battle alongside each other!", "The stars themselves must tremble at your strength, %s!", "I have rarely seen such raw, glorious power, %s! Truly worthy!", "Raise a glass, %s! For today, you are the mightiest of us all!"]

#define WrestleWin ["Stand aside, mortal. You have no business on a field of such battle.","Your courage is noted, yet your strength is but a whisper in the gale, %s.","I have struck down titans; do not feel ashamed that you have fallen, %s.","The storm has passed, little one. Find safety elsewhere.","My hammer brooks no resistance, %s. Be glad I stayed my hand.","You fight with passion, %s, but passion alone cannot weather the lightning.","A valiant effort, yet the Norns had decreed your defeat before the first blow was struck.","Return to your hearth, %s. This is a realm for those hardened by war.","You lack the true fire of an Asgardian, %s. Do not seek me out again.","Go with honor, %s. You were simply outmatched by the Son of Odin.","I have faced many who called themselves warriors, %s. You show promise, if you continue to train.","Your strike was well-timed, %s! Perhaps you shall be a warrior in the ages to come.","It is a rare day that I am engaged so earnestly! You have my respect, %s.","A sturdy blow, %s! You stand taller than many of your kin.","You yield, %s? It is a wise choice to accept the will of the thunder.","Well struck! You possess a warrior's soul, %s—that is a gift to be cherished.","By my father's beard, that was an energetic clash! You are a fine combatant, %s.","You have earned your place in this battle, %s. Would that all who faced me were so capable.","The storm bows to no one, %s, but you have made it take notice!","I am weary, yet invigorated! A worthy contest, %s.","You possess power, %s! Were you born of some celestial lineage, I might mistake you for a peer.","Truly, you have made Mjolnir sing! It has been an age since I felt such a contest.","You fight as though you were forged in the fires of Surtur himself, %s!","Your strength is like a mountain, %s. I am honored to have tested it.","You stand as a true champion, %s. May your saga be written in the halls of glory.","At last! A combatant who commands the very air we breathe, %s! A glorious duel!","You possess the might of a true hero, %s. It was a struggle of legends.","My heart thunders in my chest! You are a worthy rival indeed, %s.","Few can withstand the tempest as you have, %s. You are a giant among your people.","You are worthy of a song in Valhalla, %s. A hard-fought victory, by Odin's name!","You are an equal in might! It is a rare and terrifying joy to clash with one such as you, %s!","The earth itself trembles at our resolve! A victory to be etched in the stars, %s!","You are a warrior of the highest order, %s. The Nine Realms have few who can match us.","A battle of gods! Let this day be recorded so all may know of your strength, %s!","I have not felt such adrenaline since the wars of the Jotuns! You are unmatched, %s!"]

#define WrestleDefeat ["I... I was caught by surprise! A trick of the trickster, surely?","You have bested the God of Thunder? By what sorcery, %s?","A momentary lapse, %s. Do not think the storm has ended.","I am humbled... a lesson for the prince of Asgard.","You strike hard, mortal. My hammer feels heavy this day.","I have been bested... a result I did not foresee, %s.","Your strength is greater than I gave you credit for, %s.","I yield the field, but not my honor, %s.","You have learned the secrets of battle well, %s.","The lightning did not strike true... a failure of form, %s.","A noble victory, %s. You fight with clarity.","You have surpassed my defenses. You are a skilled warrior, %s.","My own arrogance was my undoing, %s. You have taught me a lesson.","Well earned, %s. I look forward to our next encounter.","The victory is yours. I must meditate on this outcome.","You fought with wisdom and power, %s. I concede this battle.","You are a formidable foe, %s. I am glad you are not my enemy.","My strength was met by yours, and mine was found wanting. A true warrior's win.","You possess a tactical brilliance that is rare, %s.","I am honored to have been defeated by one of such capability, %s.","You have the power of a tempest, %s! I bow to your superior combat today.","I have not felt such a blow since the days of my youth, %s.","You are a champion among champions, %s.","Truly, you have mastered the art of war, %s.","Your strength is unquestionable. A glorious victory for you, %s.","You are a titan in every sense! A defeat for me, but a triumph for your spirit, %s!","You have truly outmatched the thunder! A legendary performance, %s!","I have met my match. You are a warrior of the first rank, %s.","My pride is bruised, but my respect for you has grown tenfold, %s.","A historic clash! You have mastered the battlefield this day, %s.","You are an equal! The Nine Realms will speak of this victory for an age, %s!","You possess the might of the cosmos! I concede with honor, %s!","You have transcended the limits of mortal battle! A god-like triumph, %s!","A battle that shall echo in the halls of Valhalla! Well fought, %s!","You are the storm, and I am but the wind today. A magnificent victory, %s!"]
